    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Stages of achievement and proficiency in a discipline, course of study, art, or craft, typically reserved for an academic rank or distinction conferred by a university or college as a mark of proficiency in scholarship or skill.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
